  "title": "🗣️ Talk A Lot? Get Paid 💸 | No Desk, Just Vibes | Events & Marketing",
  "description": "<p><strong>Let’s be real.</strong><br />If you enjoy talking to people and hate sitting still all day —<br />this role might actually make sense for you.</p><p>We’re expanding our <strong>Events & Marketing Team</strong> and looking for people who are comfortable speaking to others and learning on the job.</p><p>No experience needed.<br />Training provided.<br />Just bring effort & attitude.</p><h3>🎯 What You’ll Do</h3><p>• 🎪 Represent brands at events, roadshows & pop-ups<br />• 🗣️ Talk to customers face-to-face & share promotions<br />• 🤝 Build confidence, communication & people skills<br />• 📍 Work at different locations across Singapore</p><h3>💰 What You’ll Get</h3><p>• 💸 Performance-based earnings (your effort matters)<br />• 🧠 Step-by-step training & guidance<br />• 🚀 Career progression for consistent performers<br />• 🎉 Young, energetic & supportive team</p><h3>👀 Who This Fits</h3><p>• Outgoing / talkative / energetic individuals<br />• Fresh grads / ORD / students welcome<br />• Open to learning communication & engagement skills<br />• Comfortable interacting with people</p><p>If you can talk — we can train you.</p><p>👉 <strong>Apply now.</strong><br />We’ll have a quick chat to see if it’s a fit.</p>",
